1. css/base.css
2. css/masthead.css
3. css/layout.css
4. css/landing.css
5. **css/builder.css** ← This file
6. css/preview.css
7. css/modals.css
8. css/components.css
9. css/animations.css
10. css/folders-trash.css

Since `builder.css` loads AFTER `styles.css`, its rules take precedence due to CSS cascade order.

The initial fix to `styles.css` was overridden by this file's rule.
